==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Torpedinous
<hw>Tor*ped"i*nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to a torpedo; resembling a torpedo; exerting a benumbing
influence; stupefying; dull; torpid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Fishy were his eyes; <qex>torpedinous</qex> was his manner.</q>
<rj><qau>De Quincey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Torpedo</ent>⟦br⟧
